                            <comment id="70295" author="morrone" created="Wed, 30 Oct 2013 18:26:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I would like to advocate that we completely remove the term &quot;coordinator&quot; from the document (and perhaps &quot;agent&quot; as well).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From what I have read of the document, there appears to be no reason to add a new terms beyond &quot;MDT&quot; and &quot;client&quot;.  Those fully explain to users/administrators of lustre where to run commands.  It would appear to me that &quot;coordiantor&quot; and &quot;agent&quot; are internal implentation details, and by exposing them to users we can only introduce more confusion.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
